data.description: Never run out of SPACE! This beautiful 3-bedroom 2-bath home has all the traditional amenities you would appreciate. Spacious rooms, wide staircase, big picture window, wood burning fireplace...just to name a few. Living room is bright and spacious with an abundance of natural light and is open to the dining area. The well-appointed kitchen features a center island and ample counter space. Three cozy bedrooms provide a retreat for every member of the family. Need more rooms? No problem! There is an extra area that could be an office or a 4th bedroom. The garage has been enclosed and can be 2nd living area/den or game room and includes a wet-bar.  This 2-story home is situated in a desirable neighborhood on a wide city street that offers a median with beautiful shade trees. Home is close to Glenmore Elementary and Glenmore Park. Hurry, you do not want to miss this one!
